summary: Senbonzakura is a katana from bleach!
descriptionHtml:
========
Lore !
========
Senbonzakura is a zanpakto that belong to by byakuya kuchiki , because of a mistake of tide kubo the katana fall into the wheel of time and some how appear in skyrim !

================
Where and How ?
================

Craftable in any forge with [b]Steel Smithing perk[/b] .

================

Please dont reupload this product into an other web site !

Thanks to kubo for bleach

Enjoy !
